Thank you for bringing us
a cool project.

02:30.391 --> 02:31.900
- Oh, you guys are the right
guys for this for sure.

02:32.059 --> 02:33.235
- Thank you, brother.
I appreciate it.

02:33.319 --> 02:34.895
And I understand
that it has spent some time

02:34.979 --> 02:36.313
just kind of sitting around.

02:36.397 --> 02:37.990
- It did. In 2011,
we were getting ready

02:38.149 --> 02:39.482
for Santa's Roadies.

02:39.567 --> 02:41.401
