we do every year,

02:41.485 --> 02:43.328
where we just
load up the Cadillac with toys

02:43.487 --> 02:44.746
and hit a bunch of shelters.
- Yeah.

02:44.831 --> 02:46.323
- And we hit some black ice
in Idaho

