of a rock-and-roll show.

03:04.851 --> 03:06.435
- I completely dig it.

03:06.594 --> 03:07.928
- I definitely want
to modernize her.

03:08.012 --> 03:09.271
- Okay.
- All right.

03:09.355 --> 03:10.772
- I like that.

03:10.857 --> 03:12.024
