get full 450, 500 horsepower

03:46.384 --> 03:48.393
out of an LS engine
and drive it every day.

03:48.552 --> 03:49.886
- I like it.

03:49.979 --> 03:51.813
- And it's never
gonna misbehave on you.

03:51.973 --> 03:53.398
You'll have tons of horsepower.

03:53.483 --> 03:55.725
You'll have tons
of dependability.

03:55.810 --> 03:57.477
If this was mine,
that's what I'd do.

03:57.561 --> 03:59.229
- All right,
that's what I like to here.

03:59.313 --> 04:00.730
That's why I'm here.
- Awesome. Awesome.

04:00.815 --> 04:01.648
That's what I would do.

04:01.741 --> 04:03.066
I got a pretty good idea

04:03.150 --> 04:06.078
