and tell me, what do you see?

04:09.740 --> 04:12.251
- Black, not gloss black,
but maybe, you know,

04:12.335 --> 04:13.910
some kind of a matte,
maybe a little bit of--

04:13.995 --> 04:15.328
- A little satin.
- Yeah.

04:15.421 --> 04:17.914
I see old-school flames.
- Okay, all the way down?

04:17.999 --> 04:20.759
