so we should go for it, man.

04:20.918 --> 04:22.502
- You think flames all the way
or just the front?

04:22.595 --> 04:23.920
- I'd go all the way.

04:24.013 --> 04:25.347
- You would? Okay.
- Yeah.

04:25.506 --> 04:27.590
To me, there's a way
to go all the way

04:27.675 --> 04:29.434
without doing too much.

04:29.519 --> 04:32.595
So you can do more
going on up here.

04:32.689 --> 04:35.190
And then if it just starts
to taper down, it...

04:35.275 --> 04:36.599
- I like that.

04:36.693 --> 04:38.193
- Accentuates the length
of the car.

04:38.278 --> 04:39.686
- Yeah. I can see it.

04:39.770 --> 04:41.521
- But yet it's still satin
black car with flames,

04:41.614 --> 04:43.273
as opposed to it just
being covered in the turquoise.

04:43.357 --> 04:44.783
It'd be gorgeous.

04:44.942 --> 04:45.951
- Yeah.
That's what I'm thinking.

04:46.110 --> 04:47.536
- It'd be gorgeous
and era correct.

04:47.695 --> 04:50.038
- So, Mike,
the question of the day--

04:50.123 --> 04:53.292
Obviously I'm the business guy.
- I see it coming.

04:53.376 --> 04:56.369
- So what kind of budget
are you thinking?

04:56.454 --> 04:57.954
- I think my top number
would be 80,000, all righ?

04:58.039 --> 04:59.289
- Okay.

04:59.373 --> 05:00.882
- If I could come in around
75,000...

05:01.042 --> 05:02.217
- I'm with you.

05:02.302 --> 05:03.802
- That'd be good,
but I don't want to skimp.

05:03.961 --> 05:05.971
If you guys get to a point
where we need to talk

05:06.130 --> 05:08.298
about doing something
to take it over the edge

05:08.391 --> 05:09.632
to where it needs to be,
I'm open to that.

05:09.717 --> 05:10.892
- Okay.

05:11.052 --> 05:12.802
- We'll keep it
at that right level.

05:12.887 --> 05:13.979
- All right.
