08:30.501 --> 08:31.760
you know, red, white,
blue kind of thing...

08:31.919 --> 08:33.345
- I like where you're
going with that.

08:33.429 --> 08:34.930
- Whatever you think looks best.

08:35.014 --> 08:36.339
- Absolutely.

08:36.432 --> 08:37.933
- But I think that would
look really cool.

08:38.017 --> 08:39.267
- I like that.

