but at the same time,

09:01.123 --> 09:02.699
they want a surprise at the end.

09:02.792 --> 09:04.709
I just hope we're all
on the same page.

09:04.868 --> 09:07.462
That way, his surprise at the
end isn't an unfortunate on.

